{"tid":460064,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"[理性討論]有時覺得平凡是福，但有時又不甘於平凡","createTime":"2017-11-06T10:15:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-07T02:49:50.000Z","uid":139272,"like":6,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a226ce290a019af91cdd973f7c04098f4bf1b024","tid":460064,"uid":139272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T10:15:08.000Z","msg":"平凡:<br />\n<br />\n對於生活起香港都係一個好處，<br />\n起碼人生會簡單一D，普普通通跟足社會規範<br />\n永遠唔講夢想，只係想開開心心生活，有一份穩定工作就夠<br />\n慢慢享受住平凡既樂趣!<br />\n<br />\n不甘於平凡:<br />\n<br />\n對於生活起香港，做個不甘平凡既人真係好有挑戰性，<br />\n要發展自己夢想，起香港地代價都好高(租金、高昂學費，etc)<br />\n而且一失敗你就好容易跌入萬劫不復既狀態! <br />\n例如創業，你一失敗就難搵工(空窗期太長)、欠債、分分鐘無屋你住<br />\n不過起香港呢個社會，如果因為追夢中成功而keep住做緊自己喜歡既事<br />\n其實會特別開心，起碼自己成功走出左香港社會為我地設定既框框!<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n生於香港既大家又會想做邊類人呢?<br />\n<br />\n平凡: 正評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不甘於平凡: 負評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bd2c4c6be916bc46033929810a21a912805df06","tid":460064,"uid":54387,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T10:39:10.000Z","msg":"平唔平凡無得我揀<br />\n<br />\n因為我只係一條鹹魚"},{"pid":"bb55532b9dc378cadddba330f1ae9d4af3c1fbfc","tid":460064,"uid":60793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T11:26:59.000Z","msg":"絕對不甘平凡"},{"pid":"b5975f7deef6ba5a6ebd9e18cc09184d4d5bf578","tid":460064,"uid":139272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T13:34:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>平唔平凡無得我揀<br />\n<br />\n因為我只係一條鹹魚</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打有夢想？"},{"pid":"47c4cd4cf2a377c4ac2b91ab062763ae171c22d5","tid":460064,"uid":139272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T13:35:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>絕對不甘平凡</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n想點唔平凡啊？"},{"pid":"4f6dc120b011ae70ffca8a444580c27e85a2a140","tid":460064,"uid":14440,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T13:55:26.000Z","msg":"唔係甘唔甘心既問題 係能力問題<br />\n有頭髮邊個想做癩痢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n普普通通過日子都好難架啦"},{"pid":"8ec663090adbad95e67e537f44b6fdd09e5d150c","tid":460064,"uid":45148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T14:00:27.000Z","msg":"平平凡凡買到樓<br />\n同愛人一齊住是福<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但原來買到樓就是不平凡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b92c0ace9aba31d2d55f0c8e6aac69b57534792b","tid":460064,"uid":99816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T15:29:29.000Z","msg":"唔一定要創業先不甘於平凡既，可能做到高職位，四處去公幹deal with foreigners create value to the world 都得既"},{"pid":"e77fb7a065c562c2c62b470f898f371ce4303215","tid":460064,"uid":139272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T02:48:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔係甘唔甘心既問題 係能力問題<br />\n有頭髮邊個想做癩痢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n普普通通過日子都好難架啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n睇你點定義咩叫普普通通啦<br />\nbtw能力雖然都係一個issue，但起碼仲可以後天補救嘛<br />\n不過我想講既係心態問題<br />\n因為有人即使能力未足，都會有野心想不甘平凡"},{"pid":"4e3649c4dc6092f8d4162c4229a7a3d0cd6de091","tid":460064,"uid":139272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T02:49:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>平平凡凡買到樓<br />\n同愛人一齊住是福<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">但原來買到樓就是不平凡</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n明明基本人類生存條件都竟然變左好多人既人生目標<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d57c694cf013672e379ec6d66918639f2cfa0548","tid":460064,"uid":139272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T02:49:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔一定要創業先不甘於平凡既，可能做到高職位，四處去公幹deal with foreigners create value to the world 都得既</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n都係啊，巴打邁向緊呢個目標?"}]}